{"title":"辞行","authors":["荒苇"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":8,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"辞行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别了，北平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再见，同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记着你们的嘱咐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带了人民的希望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们到西南去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到边疆去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“边区去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好好工作。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的队伍到处受人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民的欢迎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活在群众里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你会炼的更坚强！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志，不要惦念，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们没有什么牵挂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东的大旗子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抵挡过狂风暴雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东的好学生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也经得住考验！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在中原，在边疆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做的都是革命工作。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家好好干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿出成绩来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比比看！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们走了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到西南，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到边疆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在珠江三角洲上插秧苗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在云贵高原上学习苗家舞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向群众低头学习，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三年，五年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年，八年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再回到北平来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你来检阅！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}